# API 测试示例集合
# 可以导入到 Postman 或其他 API 测试工具

## 1. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

## 2. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

## 3. 获取订阅状态（需要 Token）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscription/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 4. 注册设备（需要 Token）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/device/register
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "unique-device-id-123",
  "deviceName": "Chrome on MacBook Pro",
  "deviceInfo": {
    "browser": "Chrome",
    "os": "macOS",
    "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0..."
  }
}

###

## 5. 验证设备（需要 Token）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/device/verify
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "unique-device-id-123"
}

###

## 6. 获取设备列表（需要 Token）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/device/list
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 7. 移除设备（需要 Token）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/device/unique-device-id-123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 8. 创建订阅（需要 Token）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscription/subscribe
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "premium",
  "duration": 1
}

###

## 9. 获取当前订阅（需要 Token）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscription/current
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 10. 健康检查（无需认证）
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

## 11. 根路由（无需认证）
GET http://localhost:3000/
